4. `/sessions/[threadId]/operators/page.tsx` - Operators
5. `/sessions/[threadId]/brief/page.tsx` - Research Brief
6. `/sessions/[threadId]/agents/page.tsx` - Agent Status

## Handle /sessions/new Separately
The new session page is different - it's not tied to a threadId. Options:
